Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:06.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:08.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: 'Oh' unecessary or not? I'm leaning towards yes; what do you think? - delamoo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:10.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:13.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:15.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:17.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:19.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:21.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:24.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:25.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:27.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:29.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:31.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:36.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened... to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:08.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:09.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:13.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:15.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:16.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:19.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:20.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's really no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:26.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that field of pampas grass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:27.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:35.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:37.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:42.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am holding her, but it's not what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:47.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I gave alcohol to an innocent girl and took her to a secluded place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:48.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:49.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:55.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:56.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:00.57,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:03.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it enough, but I am very sorry.
Comment: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:02.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alternative: "I deeply apologize for doing such a bad thing." Which is better?
Comment: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:02.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aware of the situation, so I became a little upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that "a little upset"? You old maid.
Comment: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:08.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,TL HAAALP: Koi says Violent intimidator? Old maid sounds terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:14.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu Kamio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:20.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks familiar.
Comment: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Seems or looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't stand out much though.
Comment: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ALTERNATIVE: I don't leave a very strong\Nimpression on people. BetteR?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we've met before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since you've been here a few times for checkups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:37.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, lots of weird things really did happen on your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that just makes it all the more memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:45.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you become friends with Kano, instead of just playing with me all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you might get along pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're both pretty weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:51.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:53.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:55.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:56.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Comment: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:56.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,ALTERNATIVE: "What's wrong?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:59.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to get my pay for today's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:00.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you wait till tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be difficult if I try to pick it up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's my-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:09.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've gone to sleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:25.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeep!
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:26.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to turn on the lights so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:29.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't properly examine you in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Kano, you've grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me in weird places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a proper clinical technique, called "palpation".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In examinations, you don't caress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:47.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:49.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I guess it was just a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have any cats here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:55.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:57.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:04:59.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kano, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:01.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:03.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong, Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:09.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:12.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating the same words, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This child is my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my only treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:23.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my precious little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:27.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:32.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Onee-chan hugging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:33.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were falling asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:37.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You came and hugged me, so I held you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:38.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:40.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to hurry up and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:43.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But can we stay like this for just a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:51.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You held me like this when Daddy passed away, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:51.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:53.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:55.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you have a nice scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, a cicada flew in through the vent again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:05.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, the soy sauce bottle fell over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, the salad oil spilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:11.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, Yukito-san's bacon and eggs went wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah-wah-wah-wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:15.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:17.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:18.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, something happened to this food, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:47.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me as if, "wow, he's actually eating it!"?
Comment: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:49.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Clumsy line above.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:49.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not looking like that, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't taste like cicadas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:14.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:18.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:19.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:20.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... this and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll see you later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:27.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:30.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:47.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least do enough to earn your wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:53.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done everything already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:54.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have something else for you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to say something, just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But a pay raise is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:06.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:07.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's about last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:11.84,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:14.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:20.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've been looking for him for a while, but I can't seem to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:21.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:31.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato... Where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's starting to set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:50.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:51.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of anywhere else to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you use your magic to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think my magic works like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was given this bandana,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to keep it on until I become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it off until then, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:25.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I take it off, I'll be able to use my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:29.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was little, so I don't remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's been wrapped around my wrist ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:37.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been troublesome at times, like during swimming and health checkups,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:40.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was even teased a few times too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, Onee-chan always saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I've been able to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:48.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:51.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come all the way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he could possibly be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukito-kun, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized where Potato is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:03.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:04.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:05.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:06.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:06.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:09.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:10.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:13.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:15.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:17.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:24.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, don't ever make me worry like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yukito-kun, how did you know that he was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... well... uh... what do you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko Pikopik-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:38.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:39.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen, Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever wander off again without telling me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:46.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you did what you say.
Comment: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:49.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alternative (maybe better): You always say you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:51.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:53.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:54.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:57.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really not remember anything about what happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:10:59.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:00.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:01.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:11.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun, will you listen to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you can tell me anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:18.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hardly remember anything about my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she was never very healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She became sick right after she gave birth to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and passed away when I was about three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:31.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad would often say, "Your mom was like you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I couldn't picture her very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:39.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but, but it's not so bad; I wasn't that lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:44.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan was like a mom to me, and dad was always around too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:57.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means that Onee-chan was without a mom for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:01.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently I realized how unfair that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:07.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was always busy with the clinic, and then he got sick himself from working too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:15.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I could do was watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:16.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, it's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:22.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan works and takes care of me, but I can't really do anything to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not much help either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:33.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could use magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:37.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would use it to meet my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet her and apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank her, not apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:54.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother is the reason that you're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone said to me, "I'm sorry that you gave birth to me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:07.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your mom, Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:18.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:22.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, she went to the same place your mom is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was looking for a girl in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:29.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Somewhere beyond this sky is a girl with wings."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my mom's favorite saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for that girl too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:38.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:45.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then someday, when I can fly, I'll look for that girl for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.89,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\fsp2\pos(646,68)\c&H091403&}KAMIO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:51.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl's in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't feeling very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:00.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were there, she wouldn't rest well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're her mother so it shouldn't bother her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm her mother, we do have other issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you aren't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I couldn't pick you up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:26.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're busy with other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like dinosaurs, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:39.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she like dinosaurs so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:40.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always liked them, ever since she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know anything about her, even though she's your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:50.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget that it was her birthday yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does that girl act strangely during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:57.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she always strange?
Comment: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:57.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blah, note to self. Not the same as Ep2 preview
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:02.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if there's nothing, then it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:08.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, enough with this trivial talk; it's finally the main event of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:12.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The erotic confessions corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did we end up going there?!
Comment: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: above line feels clumsy, but it might just be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:16.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just saying the title turns me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a pervert or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:18.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:27.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, dinosaurs thrived for millions and millions of years, but then they faced their end and went extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:31.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of sad and makes me emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:33.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still having those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:34.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In my dreams, I'm going back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:40.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to describe it, but I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:48.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the scent of the wind, the feel of the breeze on my skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:51.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the way the air moves and the passing of the seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm going back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:55.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of a dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:57.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:57.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Comment: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:13.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Same 'oh' question
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:01.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where my dreams are taking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:06.76,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:08.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:07.99,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:08.79,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to get hit by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:09.81,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:10.95,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:12.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's the 'suika wari' today, huh?
Comment: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:11.74,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,TL NOTE: 'suika wari' is watermelon cracking
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:11.74,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:12.94,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kano wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:13.96,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:15.42,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you spoiling her a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:16.75,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:18.15,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Set...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.03,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Comment: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,# Set...   (gesshoki) Replaced 376 since it made more sense. Original 376 was "Ready...".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:25.79,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's impossible to make money here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.10,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:41.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't crash into me every single time!
Comment: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:42.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: 'single' remove maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:45.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:47.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop always acting so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a little busy yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for it, you will live here from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:00.82,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:00.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:01.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:05.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with didn't you want me to leave town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He got up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't figure it out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:33.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:35.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is mysterious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:40.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such a wonderful special talent, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:42.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Clap clap clap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:48.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use a bit of what is called "magic".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:50.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many mysteries in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:56.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I have a special thank you gift.
