Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:57.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:01.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:11.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl with wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:12.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:16.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the same girl as my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:27.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a little girl, I had a picture book like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:28.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:35.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the picture book, there was a girl with pure white wings on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:42.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a little girl, I dreamt of flying through the sky with her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing strange about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:50.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if the purpose of your journey is to look for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:59.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because everyone has a destination they want to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:07.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are going to be beautiful again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:12.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:14.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it well at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A destination, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with today's homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:28.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:30.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-A-R-D-S.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:32.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:34.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:38.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to play cards with you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Play by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:46.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, we have come from a faraway planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:47.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:55.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:56.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:56.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:03.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already looked there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you two go that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:07.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, do you have any idea where she might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:10.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to look anywhere we can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:20.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.74,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:25.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:26.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:28.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:28.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:30.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pi-ka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:31.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pi-ka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he asking us to follow him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:36.35,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:36.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she said she'd already looked there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:38.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:40.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:43.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tighly clasping my only treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:43.73,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:45.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:47.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:49.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano.
