Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.91,0:23:45.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun, I am writing this to you because I think you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:49.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally decided to go to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:53.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling it will make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:58.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that I will meet the girl you are looking for too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:01.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how long it will take,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:03.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I will definitely bring her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.99,0:24:08.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be grateful if you can help Onee-chan until I return.
